namespace = SYS_Construct
country_event = { 
	id = SYS_Construct.100
	title = no_localisation
	desc = no_localisation
	picture = CITY_DEVELOPMENT_eventPicture
	is_triggered_only = yes
	hidden = yes
	immediate = { }
	option = { 
		name = PTM_EXIT
		highlight = yes
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.001
			}
		}
	}
}
country_event = {

			set_variable = {

			}

				which = nut
				value = 0
			}
			every_province = { 
				limit = { 
					AND = { 
						OR = { 
							is_city = yes
							is_colony = yes

					OR = { 
						owned_by = ROOT
						owner = { 
							AND = {

											check_variable = { 
												which = ggy
												value = 7
											}
										}

										}

										limit = { 
											check_variable = { 
												which = gho
												value = 7
											}
										}
										set_variable = { 
											which = ghn
											which = gek
										}
									}
									else = { 
										if = { 
											limit = { 
												check_variable = { 
													which = gho
													value = 3
												}
											}
											if = { 
												limit = { 
													check_variable = {

														value = 4
													}
												}

														}

														value = 60
													}

															value = 5
														}

														which = ghn
														value = 42
													}
												}
												else = { 
													set_variable = { 
														which = ghn
														value = 30
													}
												}
											}

												}
											}
										}

														value = 1

				}

						value = 0.001

					NOT = {

							which = gha
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
					NOT = {

							value = 0.001

					}
					NOT = {

							which = ghe
							value = 0.001
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = SYS_Construct.001.dtooltip
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.008
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = PTM_EXIT
		highlight = yes
	}

						}
					}
					NOT = {

										which = aro

										value = 0.001

									which = ghg
									which = ntp
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = gho
									value = 6
								}
								if = { 
									limit = { 
										check_variable = { 
											which = gho
											value = 7
										}
									}
									set_variable = { 
										which = ghn
										which = gek
									}
								}
								else = { 
									if = { 
										limit = { 
											check_variable = { 
												which = gho
												value = 3
											}
										}
										if = { 
											limit = { 
												check_variable = { 
													which = gho
													value = 4
												}
											}
											if = { 
												limit = { 
													check_variable = { 
														which = gho
														value = 6
													}
												}
												set_variable = { 
													which = ghn
													value = 60
												}
											}
											else_if = { 
												limit = { 
													check_variable = { 
														which = gho
														value = 5
													}
												}
												set_variable = { 
													which = ghn
													value = 42
												}
											}
											else = { 
												set_variable = { 
													which = ghn
													value = 30
												}
											}
										}
										else = { 
											set_variable = { 
												which = ghn
												value = 20
											}
										}
									}
									else = { 
										if = { 
											limit = { 
												check_variable = { 
													which = gho
													value = 1
												}
											}
											if = { 
												limit = { 
													check_variable = { 
														which = gho
														value = 2
													}
												}
												set_variable = { 
													which = ghn
													value = 12
												}
											}
											else = { 
												set_variable = { 
													which = ghn
													value = 6
												}
											}
										}

												which = ghn
												value = 2
											}
										}

										value = 2
									}
								}

										NOT = { 
											check_variable = { 
												which = ghg
												value = 0
											}
										}
									}
									set_variable = { 
										which = ghg
										value = 0
									}
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ggy
									value = 0
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ggy
									which = ghg
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = nut
									which = ggy
								}
								multiply_variable = { 
									which = ghg
									which = gfe
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = ghn
									value = 0
								}
								set_variable = { 
									which = gho
									value = 0
								}
							}
							else = { 
								set_variable = { 
									which = ggy
									value = 0
								}
							}
						}
						else = { 
							set_variable = { 
								which = ggy
								value = 0
							}
						}
					}
					else = { 
						set_variable = { 
							which = ggy
							value = 0
						}
					}
				}
				else = { 
					set_variable = { 
						which = gha
						value = 0
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ghb
						value = 0
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ghc
						value = 0
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ghd
						value = 0
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ghe
						value = 0
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = ggy
						value = 0
					}
				}
				PREV = { 
					change_variable = { 
						which = ghg
						which = PREV
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = nut
						which = PREV
					}
				}
			}
			else = { 
				set_variable = { 
					which = gha
					value = 0
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ghb
					value = 0
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ghc
					value = 0
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ghd
					value = 0
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ghe
					value = 0
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ggy
					value = 0
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggw
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggx
				value = 0
			}
		}
		set_variable = { 
			which = ghn
			value = 0
		}
		change_variable = { 
			which = ghn
			which = gha
		}
		change_variable = { 
			which = ghn
			which = ghb
		}
		change_variable = { 
			which = ghn
			which = ghc
		}
		change_variable = { 
			which = ghn
			which = ghd
		}
		change_variable = { 
			which = ghn
			which = ghe
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				check_variable = { 
					which = ghn
					value = 0.001
				}
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = gho
				which = ghn
			}
			divide_variable = { 
				which = gho
				which = ghg
			}
			multiply_variable = { 
				which = gho
				value = 100
			}
		}
		else = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = gho
				value = 0
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.002.a
		custom_tooltip = SYS_Construct.002.a
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.003
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.002.b
		custom_tooltip = SYS_Construct.002.b
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.004
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.002.c
		custom_tooltip = SYS_Construct.002.c
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.005
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.002.d
		custom_tooltip = SYS_Construct.002.d
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.006
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.002.e
		custom_tooltip = SYS_Construct.002.e
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.007
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = PTM_BACK
		highlight = yes
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.001
			}
		}
	}

	is_triggered_only = yes
	immediate = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = ggy
						value = 7
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ggy
					value = 7
				}
			}
			if = { 
				limit = { 
					NOT = { 
						OR = { 
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = ntp
								value = 1
							}
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = ntp
								value = 2
							}
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = ntp
								value = 3
							}
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = ntp
								value = 4
							}
							is_variable_equal = { 
								which = ntp
								value = 5
							}
						}
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = ntp
					value = 0
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.013.a
		trigger = { 
			check_variable = { 
				which = ggy
				value = 0.001
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.001
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.013.b
		trigger = { 
			is_variable_equal = { 
				which = ggz
				value = 1
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = SYS_Construct.013.btooltip
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggz
				value = 0
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggy
				value = 0
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.013.i
		trigger = { 
			is_variable_equal = { 
				which = ggz
				value = 0
			}
			always = no
		}
		custom_tooltip = SYS_Construct.013.itooltip
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggz
				value = 1
			}
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggy
				value = 0
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.013.c
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggy
				value = 1
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.013.d
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggy
				value = 2
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.013.e
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggy
				value = 3
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.013.f

				which = ggy
				value = 4
			}
			hidden_effect = {

			}
		}

				which = ggy
				value = 5
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.013.h
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggy
				value = 6
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = SYS_Construct.013.j
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = ggy
				value = 7
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = Extra_Units_More
		custom_tooltip = custom.Extra_Units_More
		trigger = { 
			NOT = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = ntp
					value = 5
				}
			}
		}
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = ntp
				value = 1
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = Extra_Units_Less
		trigger = { 
			check_variable = { 
				which = ntp
				value = 1
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = custom.Extra_Units_More
		hidden_effect = { 
			change_variable = { 
				which = ntp
				value = -1
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = Extra_Units_Reset
		trigger = { 
			NOT = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = ntp
					value = 0
				}
			}
		}
		custom_tooltip = custom.Extra_Units_Reset
		hidden_effect = { 
			set_variable = { 
				which = ntp
				value = 0
			}
			hidden_effect = { 
				country_event = { 
					id = SYS_Construct.130
				}
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = PTM_BACK
		highlight = yes
		hidden_effect = { 
			country_event = { 
				id = SYS_Construct.008
			}
		}
	}
}
